    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and bodywork to return to reliable service. The engine currently struggles to start, and there are noticeable leaks from the transmission and cooling system. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several dents and rusted panels, while the interior requires a deep clean and repair to the upholstery. This is being sold as-is, ideal for a buyer looking for a major project or a source for parts.",
