    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. Mechanically, it is very solid, featuring a smooth-running engine and a transmission that shifts reliably. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use, and the exterior retains a strong finish, though you may find a few small, typical road chips upon close inspection. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
