    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a refined driving experience that prioritizes both performance and longevity. Meticulously vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards, this automobile stands as a testament to diligent ownership and enduring quality. We invite you to secure a vehicle that perfectly balances sophisticated engineering with exceptional value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
